uk.ac.sanger.cgp.autocsa.beans

Class TraceBaseParam

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.sanger.cgp.autocsa.beans.TraceBaseParam
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class TraceBaseParam
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    TraceBaseParam - a bean of four primitives. The first (int) contains the position in the sts of the base, the second (float) contains the base quality value, the third (int) the scan index of the base peak, and fourth (int) the base intensity
    See Also:
